    "A variant of this approach would leave (parts of the) transformer encoder frozen during the training process.",
    "In this paper, we will demonstrate Approach B in Section 6.2 and Approach C in Section 7.2.",
    "In both cases, we will not use additional tabular data.",
    "These examples can be seen as a demonstration of how to build the NLP classifier of Approach A. Whilst all applications in this paper are classification tasks, regression tasks are handled in an analogous fashion.",
    "This section shows how transformer models can be used to extract features from text data to feed into regression or classification tasks."
